{WDM}}\\gtrsim\n0.7\\textrm{ keV}$, which is comparable to bounds obtained from Lyman-$\\alpha$\nmeasurements. Future 21-cm experiments will measure the global history of\nreionization and the neutral hydrogen power spectrum, which could either lead\nto stronger constraints or discovery of secret dark sector interactions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Dec 2017 19:00:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Jan 2018 10:46:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 22 Aug 2018 16:40:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-05"}
