chemistry of Titan-like exoplanets are\nrelatively insensitive to differences in host star. These findings may be\nfurther probed with future space-based facilities, like WFIRST, LUVOIR, HabEx,\nand OST.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Dec 2017 23:38:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-07"}
