. The\nabsence of bright steady emission argues against the presence of an echo from\nan event of multi-centennial duration and most, if not all, of the emission can\nlikely be explained by a limited number of relatively short (i.e. up to 10\nyears) events.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Dec 2017 11:07:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-13"}
