 may have practical importance in energy production is also\npresented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Dec 2017 12:23:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 Jan 2018 14:21:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 15 Jan 2018 09:50:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-16"}
