ible future applications of IG methods to\nthe physics of complexity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Dec 2017 16:12:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Mar 2018 07:06:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-10"}
